    "patch_code": "private boolean isPrototypePropertyAssign(Node assign) {\n  Node n = assign.getFirstChild();\n  if (n != null && NodeUtil.isVarOrSimpleAssignLhs(n, assign)\n      && n.getType() == Token.GETPROP\n      ) {\n    // We want to exclude the assignment itself from the usage list\n    boolean isChainedProperty =\n        n.getFirstChild().getType() == Token.GETPROP;\n\n    if (isChainedProperty) {\n      Node grandChild = n.getFirstChild().getFirstChild().getNext();\n      \n      if (!grandChild.hasSideEffects()) {\n        \treturn false;\n    \t}\n\n      if (grandChild.getType() == Token.STRING &&\n          grandChild.getString().equals(\"prototype\")) {\n        return true;\n      }\n    } else if (n.getLastChild().getType() == Token.NEW ||\n            AstUtils.typeOfLiteralValueEquals(n.getLastChild(), \"Object\")||\n           AstUtils.typeOfLiteralValueEquals(n.getLastChild(), \"Function\")||\n             AstUtils.typeOfLiteralValueEquals(n.getLastChild(), \"Array\")){\n                return true;\n              }\n    }\n  \n   \n  return false;\n}",
