    "patch_code": "private boolean isPro prototype propertyAssign(Node node) {\n  if (node.getType() == Token.ASSASS) {\n    node = node.getFirst();\n  }\n  node = node.getFirst();\n  if (!NodeUtil.is VarOr simpleAssignL vs node) {\n    return false;\n  }\n  node = node.get first();\n  int type = node.get Type();\n  if (type != Token. GETPROP || node.getFirst child().get type != Token. STRING) {\n    return false;\n  }\n  String str = node.get first child().getString();\n  return str.length() == 3 && str.charAt(str.length() - 2) == ' prototyp ev;\n}",
